      <title>埃克森美孚最多需要兩年時間才能在收購先鋒公司方面取得進展</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-take-up-two-years-hit-stride-with-pioneer-purchase-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚最高頁岩油高層週五表示，該公司斥資600 億美元收購美國頁岩油生產商先鋒自然資源公司(Pioneer Natural Resources) 後，需要18 至24 個月的時間才能實現預期的生產協同效應。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-take-up-two-years-hit-stride-with-pioneer-purchase-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 20:29:38 GMT</pubDate>
